No. 11-6147. John Ernest Dade, Petitioner v. United States District Court for the District of Idaho. 565 U.S. 1056, 132 S. Ct. 796,

181 L. Ed. 2d 478,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8632. November 28, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
